# Project Structure Guide

This is an AdonisJS application with TypeScript, Inertia.js, and Tailwind CSS. Here's the main structure:

- `app/` - Core application code
  - `controllers/` - Request handlers and business logic
  - `models/` - Database models
  - `middleware/` - Request middleware
  - `validators/` - Request validation rules
  - `exceptions/` - Custom exception handlers
  - `jobs/` - Background job definitions

- `resources/` - Frontend assets and views
  - `views/` - Inertia.js views and components

- `config/` - Application configuration files
- `database/` - Database migrations and seeders
- `start/` - Application startup files
- `tests/` - Test files

Key configuration files:
- [adonisrc.ts](mdc:adonisrc.ts) - AdonisJS configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [vite.config.ts](mdc:vite.config.ts) - Vite bundler configuration
